法方法，剝奪人之行動自由者，處5 年以下\r\n有期徒刑、拘役或9 千元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e5%98%89%e7%b0%a1%2c856%2c20220908%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,嘉簡,856,20220908,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉簡","JNO":"856","JDATE":"20220908","JTITLE":"妨害自由"}